      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">都人士.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼都人士，臺笠緇撮。彼君子女，綢直如髮。我不見兮，我心不說。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Those officers of the old capital,
With their hats of Tai leaves and small black caps! --
Those ladies of noble Houses.
With their hair so thick and straight! --
I do not see them now,
And my heart is dissatisfied.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
