      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·魚藻之什·005.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">都人士.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼都人士，充耳琇實。彼君子女，謂之尹吉。我不見兮，我心苑結。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Those officers of the old capital,
With their ear-plugs of xiu-stones! --
Those ladies of noble Houses,
Each fit to be called a Yin or a Ji! --
I do not see them now,
And my heart grieves with indissoluble sorrow.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-yuzao-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
